1. Go to the settings page and add your OpenAI API or GroqAI API key.
2. Add your UEX API for commodities and items.
3. Create a project on https://supabase.com, on SQL editor paste: 
      create table catalog_offers (
        id bigint generated always as identity primary key,
        item_name text not null,
        patch text default '4.7',
        location text not null,
        buy_auec bigint,
        sell_auec bigint
      );
      create index on catalog_offers (item_name);
4. Add your Supabase anon key and project URL.
5. Enable toggle on Supabase AI mode.

This will give you access to all StarCitizen items, along with an AI agent to help you locate items more easily.
Supabase is used to reduce API token usage. Without it, a single query may use around 17,000 tokens.
